#. Plugin Name
msgid "Moelog AI Q&A Links"
msgstr "Moelog AI Q&A Links"

#. Plugin Description
msgid "在每篇文章底部顯示作者預設的問題清單,點擊後開新分頁,由 AI 生成答案的靜態HTML。支持 OpenAI/Gemini,可自訂模型與提示。"
msgstr "Display a list of preset questions at the bottom of each post. When clicked, opens a new tab with AI-generated answers as static HTML. Supports OpenAI/Gemini with customizable models and prompts."

