#: moelog-ai-geo.php - STM Mode Settings
msgid "提供結構化資料（QAPage、Breadcrumb）、Canonical/Robots 與快取策略，幫助搜尋與 AI 爬蟲「正確解析」AI 答案頁。"
msgstr "Provides structured data (QAPage, Breadcrumb), Canonical/Robots and caching strategies to help search engines and AI crawlers correctly parse AI answer pages."

#: moelog-ai-geo.php
msgid "此功能不保證索引或排名，預設為 noindex；僅在啟用 STM 模式時採用 index,follow 並輸出對應中繼資料與 Sitemap。"
msgstr "This feature does not guarantee indexing or ranking. Default is noindex; only when STM mode is enabled will it use index,follow and output corresponding metadata and Sitemap."

